data.description: Boat Town USA!! Beautiful and well maintained canal front home right on Lakeshore Dr. Enjoy the sunrise over the lake and sunset over the canal. Never miss one again! 50' of Seawall with direct access to Lake St Clair. 3 bedroom, 2 full baths, currently configured as a 4 bedroom with formal dining room. Easily customizable to 3 bed with Living Room and Family room. Turn key! Everything is updated in the last 4 years, Dimensional Shingles, High Efficiency Furnace, new driveway, central air, the list goes on. 30 mins to Downtown Detroit by boat or by car. L'Anse Creuse Schools, bus right to the door for K-12! Bike Path to Lake St Clair Metro Park. Nice deep yard. Immediate occupancy!
